---
title: Brisket Style Beef in Red Wine Sauce with Mashed Potato and Green Beans
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Brisket Style Beef in Red Wine Sauce in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R08_W17_UK_HVP21125-3_Main_low-c1ff6b26.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/65d5afc07597174e16c1005a.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
servings: 2
author: Lily Stevens
